ivardefs.name: packageId
ivardefs.desc: The NPM package name for the Implementation Guide that this IG depends on.

ivardefs.name: uri
ivardefs.desc: A canonical reference to the Implementation guide for the dependency.

ivardefs.name: version
ivardefs.desc: The version of the IG that is depended on, when the correct version is required to understand the IG correctly.

properties.desc: Another implementation guide that this implementation depends on. Typically, an implementation guide uses value sets, profiles etc.defined in other implementation guides.
